      </font>
    </p>

    <p>
      <font face="Trebuchet MS,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="-1" color="#363636">
        You've now had your account for several days, and we hope that you're as excited as ever about your business idea. This is a great opportunity to really dig in and start the business that you've always dreamed of.
      </font>
    </p>
    <p>
      <font face="Trebuchet MS,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="-1" color="#363636">
        As you've been filling out your personal checklist, have you taken advantage of the
        <font face="Trebuchet MS,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="-1" color="#FA9B31">
          <strong>
            <%= link_to "Resources", "http://wibo.wickedstart.com/public_home", :style => "color:#FA9B31; text-decoration:none;" %>
          </strong>
        </font>
