        <font face="Trebuchet MS,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="-1" color="#FA9B31">
          <strong>
            <%= link_to "Templates", "http://wibo.wickedstart.com/public_home", :style => "color:#FA9B31; text-decoration:none;" %>
          </strong>
        </font>
        ? We've tried to make it easy for you to find great guidance and time savings so you can focus on what you really care about - implementing your business idea.
      </font>
    </p>

    <p>
      <font face="Trebuchet MS,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="-1" color="#363636">
        My business coach told me this Taoist saying: "People usually fail when they are on the verge of success. Give as much care at the end as at the beginning, and then there will be no failure".
        You've invested time and energy thinking about your idea, so keep these words of wisdom close to you as you continue on you path to entrepreneurship and launch you business successfully.
      </font>
    </p>

    <p>
      <font face="Trebuchet MS,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="-1" color="#363636">
        Remember, we're here to help you get going! If you need help, ask a question in the
        <font face="Trebuchet MS,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif" size="-1" color="#FA9B31">
          <strong>
            <%= link_to "Community", "http://wibo.wickedstart.com/public_home", :style => "color:#FA9B31; text-decoration:none;" %>
          </strong>
        </font>
